---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title={`Responsible Gaming â€“ brucewaynee`} description="18+ only. Practice responsible play. This portal does not host or operate games.">
  <section class="space-y-6">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Responsible Gaming</h1>
    <p class="text-white/80 max-w-3xl">This is an informational portal for adults (18+). Play responsibly and take breaks. We do not host or operate any games.</p>

    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="card p-5">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg">Guidelines</h2>
        <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/70 list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Set time limits and stick to them</li>
          <li>Never share personal or sensitive information</li>
          <li>Use strong device security and trusted networks</li>
          <li>If play stops being fun, step away</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-5">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg">External Resources</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-2">Find more information on healthy digital habits from reputable organizations and local guidance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-lg">Legal & Hosting Notice</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/70 mt-2">We do not manage payments, accounts, or gameplay. All titles listed are third-party experiences accessed via external links set to open in new tabs.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
